The paper deals with the combination of OFDM and large-scale antenna systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The proposed approach also involves precoding techniques, which are commonly used in control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of simulation results, which suggests a potential connection to multimedia (cs.MM) and communication systems (cs.COM).
